    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "a tiny chaotic party lol. ok so what i dont get is, if it's just a chemical thing, why does it feel so much like something is actually bothering my muscles? like is it just the acid itself or is something else physically getting in the way of the muscle working right?",
      "source": "evaluator"
